{"tid":2289888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劍指中國 日澳首領達成軍事同盟基本協議","createTime":"2020-11-17T14:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T15:39:10.000Z","uid":337052,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0362fd139e0bb7fffc5b0dd550a5eaba23403b1a","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"詳訊：日澳首腦就部隊訓練RAA達成基本協議<br />\n共同社  - 22:53<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.kyodonews.net/chinese/public/images/posts/e7b0d2530339d4a7343e9219c01fe5e8/photo_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kyodonews.net%2Fchinese%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fposts%2Fe7b0d2530339d4a7343e9219c01fe5e8%2Fphoto_l.jpg&h=6e5ac4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  【共同社11月17日電】<span class=\"red\">日本首相菅義偉17日與澳大利亞總理莫里森在官邸會談。考慮到在西太平洋等擴大軍事活動的中國，兩人就強化安全保障合作達成了一致。</span>在會談後的聯合記者會上，還透露已經就簽署有關自衛隊與澳軍聯合訓練等的《互惠准入協定》（RAA）達成基本協議。兩國首腦發表聯合聲明，就南海局勢強調&ldquo;再次確認強烈反對加劇緊張的威脅性嘗試，共享了對包括軍事化和彈道導彈發射等嚴重事件的關切&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  受新冠疫情全球蔓延的影響，日本首相最後一次在國內與外國首腦會談是今年2月，之後就一直中斷，對於9月就任的菅義偉而言，這次是首次。菅義偉就任首相後的首個電話會談對象也是莫里森。<br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">日本把澳大利亞定位為&ldquo;准同盟國&rdquo;</span>，希望通過RAA規定聯合訓練中在對方國家逗留的隊員的刑事審判權等，讓部隊往來變得順暢，強化防務合作。若能實現，<span class=\"red\">澳大利亞將是首個與日本締結RAA的國家。日本與美國之間有《日美地位協定》，規定了駐日美軍等的法律地位、基地的管理和運用等。</span><br />\n<br />\n  聯合聲明就東海局勢表示，強烈反對謀求改變現狀、加劇緊張的威脅性單方面行為。內容還商定圍繞明年實施日澳外長防長磋商（2+2）和自衛隊從平時起保護艦艇等的&ldquo;武器等防護&rdquo;對象追加澳軍推進協調，並就對香港局勢的重大關切達成共識。<br />\n<br />\n  菅義偉在記者會上強調RAA的意義稱其&ldquo;強力支撐日澳為地區和平與穩定做貢獻的意志&rdquo;。他表示：&ldquo;將共同致力於實現自由開放的印度太平洋&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  莫里森評價RAA達成基本協議是&ldquo;特別巨大的一步&rdquo;，對分別與美國是同盟關係的日澳兩國加深安全保障和經濟領域的合作表達積極意願。<br />\n<br />\n  關於菅義偉內閣提出到2050年實現溫室氣體淨零排放的目標，雙方商定推進氫能源合作。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/11/58844350e387-raa.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F11%2F58844350e387-raa.html&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM44jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=d03009c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/11/58844350e387-raa.html</a>"},{"pid":"6ec6d33b54308464191caaee74c1da87b46cc805","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">調查顯示近9成日本人對中國印象不好</span></strong><br />\n共同社 共同社, 日中關係 3 小時前 - 20:40<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.kyodonews.net/chinese/public/images/posts/7e119cff911d7ba6cb2dae90330246e2/photo_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kyodonews.net%2Fchinese%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fposts%2F7e119cff911d7ba6cb2dae90330246e2%2Fphoto_l.jpg&h=f73bdd90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  【共同社11月17日電】日本民間非營利團體&ldquo;言論NPO&rdquo;和中國國際出版集團17日公佈了在兩國實施的聯合民意調查結果。<span class=\"red\">其中對中國印象&ldquo;不好&rdquo;的日本人較去年上升5.0個百分點至89.7%，印證了對華感情的惡化。</span>每4名中國人中有3人認為&ldquo;日中關係重要&rdquo;，而日本人則自2005年開始調查以來首次跌破7成。<br />\n<br />\n  言論NPO的代表工藤泰志分析稱：&ldquo;日本對尖閣諸島（中國稱釣魚島）問題和新冠病毒疫情上的中方應對加深疑慮。另一方面，似乎中國因美中對立而寄希望於對日關係的改善。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  對中國有&ldquo;好&rdquo;印象的日本人僅為10.0%，下降5.0個百分點。這一年裡對中國印象&ldquo;變壞&rdquo;的回答增加14.2個百分點至37.0%。作為對中國印象不好的理由（多選），最多的是&ldquo;侵犯尖閣諸島週邊日本領海、領空&rdquo;，達到57.4%。<br />\n<br />\n  對日本有&ldquo;好&rdquo;印象的中國人為45.2%。&ldquo;不好&rdquo;為52.9%，與去年基本持平。作為印象不好的理由，最多的是&ldquo;對侵略歷史不道歉、不反省&rdquo;，達到74.1%。<br />\n<br />\n  認為&ldquo;日中關係重要&rdquo;的中國人增加7.7個百分點至74.7%，而日本人則減少8.5個百分點至64.2%。<span class=\"red\">回答稱&ldquo;應儘早實現首腦互訪&rdquo;的日本人佔18.8%，反映出對延期的中國國家主席習近平訪日的期待感很低。</span><br />\n<br />\n  該調查迄今已是第16次實施。在9至10月期間，有1000名日本人和1571名中國人作答。（完）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/11/b4caeb750a25-9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F11%2Fb4caeb750a25-9.html&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM44jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=14191e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/11/b4caeb750a25-9.html</a>"},{"pid":"7b8e0a05fdf74556311a2d5176fef71a8c0fdce7","tid":2289888,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"直接變六眼啦"},{"pid":"596dc30dd68e7a01166444deded0980e1a1c817c","tid":2289888,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"同盟國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd08ff7fabdcead3b2071021b071675ed9b7b92","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b8e0a05fdf74556311a2d5176fef71a8c0fdce7","tid":2289888,"uid":51583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"直接變六眼啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2705000/2709545/290720_16_v1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2705000%2F2709545%2F290720_16_v1_1024.jpg&h=b87a700b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8da09da5f358c8ece16a2adc4e5d9ef07baf3fd","tid":2289888,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"咁就岩喇 之後冇美國帶頭 你地要乖乖地自己搞嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d9af3b68f84cdc1f1bb9724620e34a69d97f1d","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"596dc30dd68e7a01166444deded0980e1a1c817c","tid":2289888,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"同盟國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/images/imageDir/ceae04cb6a2736a88be44214348de7ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Fimages%2FimageDir%2Fceae04cb6a2736a88be44214348de7ec.png&h=fd071507&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12c4b60da89d36b80a51c937787b2e0790122ef","tid":2289888,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"仲以為日本企我地中國呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢頭同我地簽貿易協議<br />\n嗰頭同人地簽軍事協議"},{"pid":"2ed0854b808746bb30542783155cfba8aaaa29d6","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e12c4b60da89d36b80a51c937787b2e0790122ef","tid":2289888,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"仲以為日本企我地中國呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢頭同我地簽貿易協議<br />\n嗰頭同人地簽軍事協議"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"賺支那的錢<br />\n繼續圍堵支那"},{"pid":"bc70bba27c5ca7f59ec87684febfb4d1e8064500","tid":2289888,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"皇軍來，我帶路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486d7f1f18122dcf25dec99074502d27ee58bfcc","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">日澳總理加強合作抗中 推動簽署軍事聯合訓練協定</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/11/17 23:13<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者楊明珠東京17日專電）<span class=\"red\">日本首相菅義偉今天會晤來訪的澳洲總理莫里森。菅義偉會後透露，雙方大致達成協議，將推動日本自衛隊與澳洲軍方簽署聯合訓練等協定，並互允雙方部隊和武器更便利入境對方。</span><br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報導，今天抵達日本進行兩天訪問的莫里森傍晚到日本首相官邸（行政中心）與菅義偉舉行會談。<br />\n<br />\n這是菅義偉9月16日上台執政以來首度在日本國內與海外的領導人舉行會談。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉在會談時表示，日澳兩國是共享基本價值與戰略利益的特別戰略夥伴，日澳關係的重要性逐漸增高，希望兩國為了實現自由且開放的印度太平洋構想能加強合作。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森（Scott Morrison）則回應說，日澳兩國是共享自由與民主志同道合的國家，肩負著特別的責任。日澳兩國能追求自由，建立以市場為核心的經濟，長年以來保持良好的關係，這讓他感到很欣慰。<br />\n<br />\n兩人在舉行會談後出席聯合記者會。菅義偉透露了兩人大致上達成協議，將推動日本自衛隊與澳洲軍方簽署聯合訓練等協定。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉說，這項協定可貢獻印度太平洋地區的和平與穩定，讓日澳兩國的意志更為堅定。莫里森表示，簽署國防合作協定大致上達成協議，堪稱立下新的里程碑，能締結那麼重要的協定證明兩國具有互信關係。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉與莫里森還發表聯合聲明。其中，日本基於安全保障相關法，日本自衛隊將把澳洲軍隊列為守護他國艦艇等的「武器等防護」對象。日澳兩國希望明年能早一點召開外交國防部長級會議（2加2會議）。<br />\n<br />\n有關經濟方面合作，針對日、澳、紐西蘭與東南亞國協等15國15日簽署區域全面經濟夥伴協定（RCEP），日澳聯合聲明中記載，樂見簽署這項協定，為了促進貿易、投資，加強印太地區的產業供應鏈是很重要的。<br />\n<br />\nNHK報導，日澳兩國對於中國在東海、南海加強海洋行動強烈不安，因此菅義偉與莫里森舉行這場會談。<br />\n<br />\n兩國彼此將關係列為「特別戰略夥伴」關係，將與美國、印度等國加強合作，以期實現「自由且開放的印度太平洋」。日澳將關注中國的動向，加強安全保障、經濟領域等的合作，以期有助於地區的和平與安定。<br />\n<br />\n日本經濟新聞報導，一旦日澳簽署國防合作協定生效，彼此的部隊基於聯合軍演的目的入境對方國時，將不需審核文件。用於軍演的武器、車輛等裝備品運至對方國的手續可簡化。為了促使日本自衛隊與澳洲軍方的往來更順利，聯合軍演的機會將增加。<br />\n<br />\n至今，日澳之間的國防合作是以日本海上及航空自衛隊，與澳洲海軍和空軍的聯合演訓為主。日澳簽署國防合作協定的話，預料將使擁有電子戰部隊的日本陸上自衛隊與澳洲軍方交流更活絡。（編輯：韋樞）1091117<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011170388.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202011170388.aspx&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM44jsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=4561aaed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202011170388.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5ea75552839abfa6ce70cfbf9a3918ad84d915bf","tid":2289888,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"有幸目睹歷史"},{"pid":"0bd985eae187fe13980f3b5b04d5d73964c90f60","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"日本把澳大利亞定位為&ldquo;准同盟國&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ae69de1b064e97fa25b0245682c7054b253eb827","tid":2289888,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142639599fa76056cac05c55cc7692082af260e6","tid":2289888,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"係咪已鋪定Biden奶共嘅後路？"},{"pid":"8c673b847b9106a3c7ab84f47a71e422f2a2fa0a","tid":2289888,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"但又簽RCEP代表咩？"},{"pid":"2aa8965f87e5426ecdf64d4e56486485ff73a1df","tid":2289888,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c673b847b9106a3c7ab84f47a71e422f2a2fa0a","tid":2289888,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"但又簽RCEP代表咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"賺支那的錢<br />\n買武器繼續圍堵支那"}]}